@RecordingStudio.BookingEngine.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5237

### Valid booking (on a 30-min boundary, 2 hours)
POST {{RecordingStudio.BookingEngine.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studioId": 1,
  "startDateTime": "2026-07-20T14:00:00",
  "durationHours": 2
}

### Invalid start time (14:15 is not on a 30-min boundary)
POST {{RecordingStudio.BookingEngine.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studioId": 1,
  "startDateTime": "2026-07-20T14:15:00",
  "durationHours": 2
}

### Invalid duration (only 1 hour)
POST {{RecordingStudio.BookingEngine.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studioId": 1,
  "startDateTime": "2026-07-20T14:00:00",
  "durationHours": 1
}